<p class="bac">
To improve your experience throughout the programme, training and learning opportunities include: 
</p>
<ul class="bac">
	<li>Classroom instruction prior to assignment </li>
	<li>Senior Speaker events, featuring presentations by top executives</li>
	<li>Constructive feedback sessions through performance evaluations </li>
	<li>Access to the online learning network for continuing education</li>
	<li>A peer and senior mentoring programme</li>
</ul>

